description.en: Diamond Launch is an IDO protocol designed to provide users and investors with cryptocurrency projects, offering token sales for early stage, premium projects. Diamond Launch offers multiple token sales as a multi-chain IDO distribution platform, allowing investors to participate more equitably in cryptocurrency pre-sales.
